What is the projected market size & growth rate of the Polyethylene Wax Market?

Market Analysis and Size

The pharmaceutical and petroleum and the refining industry's significant presence are estimated to improve polyethylene wax usage rates over the forecasted period. Furthermore, significant expansion in the petroleum business worldwide is supporting the polyethylene wax industry's manufacturing side. Consequently, the market is estimated to grow significantly over the forecasted period.

Data Bridge Market Research analyses that the polyethylene wax market which was USD 1.21 billion in 2022, is expected to USD 1.69 billion by 2030, and is expected to undergo a CAGR of 4.9% during the forecast period of 2023 to 2030.

“High density polyethylene wax” dominates the type segment of the polyethylene wax market due to its versatile applications in various industries, including plastics, coatings, and adhesives, offering excellent performance and cost-effectiveness.

